after each sentence

*Sto* je ovo? (What is this?) 
*Sto* godina traje ta veza? (How many years has this relationship lasted?)
*Oni su se odlučili da putuju *sto* kilometara. (They decided to travel a hundred kilometers.)
*Naši su se sastali da diskutuju *sto* minuta. (Our group met to discuss for a hundred minutes.)
*Koliko je *sto* evra? (How much is a hundred euros?)
*Ne smem da izgubim *sto* sekundi. (I can't afford to lose a hundred seconds.)